				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13973245</guid>
				<title>SCP-5127</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13973245/scp-5127</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 09 Jan 2021 04:24:03 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>GreenBlob</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6117650</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The article is ok, though in many aspects could be improved, the foundation takes on a clinical tone in articles and idioms are usually not used in the tone, clinical tone is meant to be specific.</p> <p>The rosy glasses are interesting but it is kind of like a regular anomalous object, the object just gives a rush of dopamine but it is just a pair of magical glasses that makes the wearer happy and doesn't really warrant an article, just contained on one of the security lockers with the key being held by a researcher and having an entry in the list of anomalous objects</p> <p>I still believe that there's potential in here though, maybe add to it more? Take it more in a direction of your choosing.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
