img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=280452&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610150934" alt="Tarage" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=280452)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tarage" >Tarage</a></span><br /> <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4263">SCP-4263</a>: Gemini</strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610150934" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" >Tanhony</a></span></p> <p>Tales directly referenced:</p> <p><strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/empire-of-dirt-part-3">Empire of Dirt (Part 3</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djoric" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=388108&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610150934" alt="Djoric" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=388108)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djoric" >Djoric</a></span><br /> <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/grant-request-for-utilization-of-electro-thaumic-computers-t">GRANT REQUEST FOR UTILIZATION OF ELECTRO-THAUMIC COMPUTERS TO PERFORM EXORCISMS OF DEMONIC ENTITIES</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610150934" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" >GreenWolf</a></span></p> 
