					<![CDATA[
						 <p>How's that for a clickbait title? It's legit, though.</p> <p>Dr. Roget, Director Gillespie, Theodore Anderson and Site-77 belong to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rjb-r" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609822950" alt="RJB_R" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rjb-r" >RJB_R</a></span>.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4558017&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609822950" alt="Grigori Karpin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4558017)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" >Grigori Karpin</a></span> for the excellent crit, as always.</p> <p>Oh, yes, I do know that's not how parent pages are supposed to work! I'm just doing that for these tales before I can upload the series hub, which is&#8230; uh&#8230; now, actually.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
